{"tid":2458542,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭叻「深入敵陣」撐黃店澳牛 網民：一切在心中","createTime":"2021-03-23T13:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T06:51:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d1482faf4b6e058ba7e2abf4f716f52580cfaa1b","tid":2458542,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/B9_01KQw88BlzTJ-1EzJvHk21mU=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A5WJJLA7LFD5RKZ3VXFJP7N7ZY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FB9_01KQw88BlzTJ-1EzJvHk21mU%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA5WJJLA7LFD5RKZ3VXFJP7N7ZY.jpg&h=b6de5cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現年70歲的陳百祥（阿叻），前年社會運動期間，多次高調表態撐警撐政府，屬根正苗紅的藍絲藝人之一。天生愛熱鬧的阿叻，早前多次被目睹疑違限聚令，三五成群約埋開餐狂歡，不過今日邵子風在facebook上載了一張阿叻獨自坐在茶記一角，形單隻影地嘆茶。再望吓邵子風的留言「朋友今朝影到！感恩叻哥支持黃店澳牛！一切在心中！」並hashtag了「手足請廣傳」、「我們並不孤單」、「叻哥有您真好」字句。<br />\n<br />\n需知道，位於佐敦的澳洲牛奶公司，除了光速餐出名外，亦是黃色商店，以往亦有響應「三罷」，如今阿叻竟公然撐黃店，有網民留言思疑阿叻「身在曹營心在漢」，亦有人說阿叻夠膽單入匹馬「深入敵陣」，情操高尚值得推崇。不過亦有網民笑阿叻「人一藍腦便殘」，為了醫肚，盲舂舂走入黃店都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n除了阿叻外，其實過往亦有藍絲die hard fans李力持曾經幫襯澳牛，嘆完茶不忘在facebook貼出相片，留言話「澳牛開返！」當時就有網民說︰「李大導，原來你係藍皮黃心，雖然你表面上罵示威者曱甴，但原來暗地裏，你係咁默默地支持我哋班黃絲，真係怪錯了你」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wP8VWMTUfqWHxzIa3cTx_RDgM10=/802x1392/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BVVGXWK5OJG3VPTPXMZPS6K2JQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwP8VWMTUfqWHxzIa3cTx_RDgM10%3D%2F802x1392%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBVVGXWK5OJG3VPTPXMZPS6K2JQ.JPG&h=c985ab70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bH2ZBUkirnLR-ARFnDompRVwD-g=/802x496/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LMVK25SBVFA6XNG652T7UG2V6M.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FbH2ZBUkirnLR-ARFnDompRVwD-g%3D%2F802x496%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLMVK25SBVFA6XNG652T7UG2V6M.JPG&h=33a842b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210323/OTX3E2KCNVFTHHQ4YXQK2CMOIA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210323%2FOTX3E2KCNVFTHHQ4YXQK2CMOIA%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97TC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=3975cb95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210323%2FOTX3E2KCNVFTHHQ4YXQK2CMOIA%2F&h=26cca8fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210323/OTX3E2KCNVFTHHQ4YXQK2CMOIA/</a>"},{"pid":"73500fb1b40e4d397b4a76164da3531a1217bbe3","tid":2458542,"uid":31215,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:26:06.000Z","msg":"黃藍是政見，好食是良知 (對藍嗰啲)<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ae71d5d305a1281adf4fd07da9c6ceee5039ab3","tid":2458542,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"世界仔未呢d <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee143995791ab117001fbba24ae4aca470e8efb","tid":2458542,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ae71d5d305a1281adf4fd07da9c6ceee5039ab3","tid":2458542,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"世界仔未呢d <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:29:25.000Z","msg":"叻哥自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5056059316c411dcc1bc81695946a08120c71a1","tid":2458542,"uid":72863,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"reply